                           Release and Personal Notes:
                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
              Well folks yet another quality release from CASAware!
              This is an RPG about a student set out to kill one of
              his teachers (Mr. Mckee, then again you probably know
              that from the title).  This hilarious game is alot of
              fun.  Although the graphics are shit, the storyline
              somewhat makes up for it.

              I wanted to extend my thanks to Dr Shoe for this
              release, not bad, then again, not that great either!
              Thanks for the game though, hope you can get more
              soon! :)

              A shout to Dr Shoe, thanks for the release, Sinful
              Vision this is the last NFO you're going to be in,
              Houdini, when's the next release coming?, Qui Tri,
              thanks for pulling us out of the drought, and to all
              other group members, thanks for your support!

                                                        - Kayden

              Personal greets to: Dr Shoe, Hitler (nice ascii),
                                  Yellow Man, Fuzzy Logic and
                                  Nowhere Man (when's the board
                                  going back up?), and of course
                                  Voodoo Child (thanks).

